%h1 Blocitoff: Self-Destructing To-do Lists
.jumbotron
  %p Feel free to create a free account and explore the world of Blocitoff.
  - if user_signed_in?
    =link_to "My Lists", root_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-lg'
  - else
    =link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-success btn-lg'
    =link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-lg'
.row
  .col-md-6
    %h4 Create To-Do Lists! Keep track of your life.
  .col-md-6
    %h4 Items self-destruct after 7 days. If it's not done, it's not important.
